title: Cotton styling skirt
detail: Calf-length skirt in lightweight woven cotton. The crossbody front body has a large lace-up on one side and a hidden buttonhole on the other. The cup is shaped at the back and the horizontal flap. This skirt is made of cotton, a soft and flexible natural fiber harvested.

title: Woven mini skirt
detail: Woven mini skirt with deep V-neck and hidden zip fastening at the front. Wide, elbow-length sleeves, stretch seams at waist and seamless cross-cut skirt. No lining. This skirt is made of Polyamide, also known as nylon, is a synthetic fiber made from petroleum.

title: Lace up slip dress
detail: Sleeveless calf-length woven viscose dress with slim, adjustable shoulder straps, square neck, and slim upper. Hidden zipper on one side, slightly flared skirt and thin tie at the waist to help flatter the figure when wearing.

title: Wrinkled dress with drawstring
detail: Crewd jersey mini dress with slim top and slim shoulder straps. V-neck with drawstring crossed in the back and tied at the front. Ribbed seams at waist and flared skirt. This dress is a combination of nature color, white, blue, and green, along with flower pattern.

title: Balloon sleeveless backless dress
detail: A woven short dress with a round neck and partially open back with a fine tie at the top. Balloon long sleeves are trimmed and slim at the wrists and waist. The skirt is a bit frayed. Partially lined.

title: Blended linen dress
detail: Knee-length dress in linen and woven cotton with a heart-shaped cup-neck and slim, adjustable shoulder straps. The back of the dress is sewn with large pleats, the ruched seams at the waist and the flared skirt. There is a lining.

title: Beige Shorts x Brown T-Shirt
detail: Regular-fit shorts in a woven cotton. Concealed drawstring and covered elastic at waistband, side pockets, and welt back pockets with button. Cotton and linen blends combine the softness of cotton with the sturdiness of linen, creating a textured fabric.

title: Khaki x Polo Shirt
detail: Slim-fit polo shirt in waffled, cotton-blend jersey. Ribbed collar, button placket, and short sleeves. Straight-cut hem with small slit at sides. This polo shirt is made of 51% of cotton and 49% of polyester.

title: White short x Beige T-shirt
detail: The overall ensemble exudes a sense of youthful energy and a playful summer vibe. It is an excellent choice for those who want to make a fashionable statement while staying comfortable and trendy. Can be styling with a cap and sandal.

title: Tank top x grey pants
detail: A ribbed tank top with a smooth feel and comfortable fit plus DRY technology. Simple and versatile. Material with a casual texture featuring DRY technology. Ribbed fabric creates a flattering fit. Great for a variety of situations from active sports to vacation wear.

title: Beach short x black T-shirt
detail: The beach shorts, with their comfortable and lightweight fabric, provide the perfect balance between comfort and functionality. Paired with a black t-shirt, allowing you to effortlessly transition from a beachside hangout to a beachfront caf√©.

title: Beach short x fabric shirt
detail: The combination of a beach short and a fabric shirt creates a stylish and comfortable outfit for a day by the ocean. The shirt adds a touch of sophistication, making it suitable for both beachside strolls and beachfront gatherings.
